\id MAT Ignatius Surum (Mikarup dialect); typed by Jill Weatherhead; exegesis checked by Marsha, Ignatius and Siria Jan-Mar 2001; transferred to Ariap dialect Aug 03 by Siria; Ariap revisions typed by John Relyea Aug 03; reviewed and extensively revised for Ariap dialect by Francis and Marsha Sep 03; comprehension check by Ariap dialect speakers-Gabi Afangi, Irwin Kuabe, John Obnadum, with John Relyea Sep-Oct 03; consultant check Nov 03 Mike Sweeney, John Stanley, Asefi, Berama, and Steven Dazim, John and Marsha. Revised by Aruamu translation team in 2019-2020, with input from many Aruamus. 
\h Matyu 
\toc3 MT 
\toc2 Matyu 
\toc1 Matyu Osirizir Akar Aghuim 
\mt1 Matyu Osirizir Akar Aghuim 
\mt2 O 
\mt1 Matyu 
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim 
\ip Matyu Osirizir Akar Aghuim, a 4plan ak…®nafaribar tong…®n faragha zui. Egha ak…®nafarir 4plan kaba, da Iesus…®n Akar Aghuim m…®g…®a, egha dughiar Iesus nguazim…®n ikiava amir bizir otivizibagh eghari. 
\ip Matyun ak…®nafarim, a Maria Iesus batezir dughiam…®n otivizir bizibagh egharava, egha ghua dughiar me Iesus m…®soghez…® an aremezim…®n tu. Egha a ua mozim…®n d…®kavigha, uan adarazi ategha God…®n Nguibam…®n ghuavanabo. 
\ip Ez…® bizir ekiar mam Matyu anekakaghasa, a kamak…®n, Iesus bizir God fom…®ra d…®k…®r…®zir akam…®n dagh amigha g…®fa. Me Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir Ghurim…®n da osiriz…®, da iti. God akam ak…®righa ghaze, a Israelia ua me inis…® gumazitam amadaght…® a izam. Ez…® ak…®nafarir kam kamagh…®n en aka, Iesus a gumazir kamra. Egha Matyun ak…®nafarir otevir av…®rav…®rir mabar, akaba kamagh…®n e m…®g…®a ghaze, bizir Iesus amiziba, da bar m…®g…®r…®g…®ar God…®n akam n…®gha izir gumaziba fom…®ra m…®kemezir akabar m…®raram otivigha g…®fa. N…® vez…®n kabar gan: Matyu 1:22-23, 2:4-6, 2:14-15, 2:23, 4:13-16, 8:16-17, 12:15-21, 13:34-35, 21:2-5, 21:16, 26:24, 26:31, 26:54, 27:6-10…®n gan. 
\ip Ez…® bizir ekiar igharazir mam, Matyun ak…®nafarim a m…®gei, a God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n m…®gei. God kamagh…®n ifonge, Iesus…®n ingangarim…®n God bar gumazamizibar atrivim…®n ikiasa, eght…® gumazamiziba bar an ifongiam…®n g…®n mangam. 
\ip Matyun ak…®nafarim…®n aven, Iesus m…®kemezir akar ruarir 5pla, da iti. Faragha zuim, a sapta 5, 6 ko, 7…®n iti, kar akar Iesus m…®ghs…®ar mam gis…®n ikia, m…®kemeziba. Akar kam a guizbang…®ra God gumazamizibar arazibar en aka. Ez…® namba 2…®n akar ruarim, a sapta 10…®n iti. Kar akar Iesus uan suren gumazibagh an…®ngizim. Dughiar kam, me mang…®va Iesus…®n akam gumazamizir igharazibav k…®masa, ez…® Iesus me mang…® damuamin bizibav gei. 
\ip Ez…® namba 3…®n akar ruarim, a sapta 13…®n iti, Iesus God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n akar is…®n zuibar gumazamizibav gei. Ez…® namba 4…®n akar ruarim, a sapta 18…®n iti, Iesus gumazamizir guizbang…®ra an suren gumazibar itir arazibar gun m…®gei. Egha namba 5…®n akar ruarim, a sapta 24 ko 25…®n iti, Iesus Dughiar Abuananam…®n bizibar gun m…®gei. 
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam uab…®, gumazir ak…®nafarim osirizim…®n gun m…®kemezir puvat…®. Ak…®nafarir kam kamagh…®n ziar kam ini, Matyu Osirizir Akar Aghuim. Guizbang…®ra, me ti dag…®aba isir gumazim Matyu, a g…®n…®ghn…®si. (N…® Matyu 9:9-13…®n gan.) 
\c 1  
\ms1 Iesus nguazir kam…®n oto 
\mr (Sapta 1:1--4:16) 
\s1 Iesus…®n inaziba ko ovavibar ziaba 
\r (Luk 3:23-38) 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Jenesis 22:18; 1 Eghaghaniba 17:11\x*Kar Krais Iesus…®n inaziba ko ovavibar eghaghanim. Iesus a Devit…®n ovavim. Ez…® Devit Abraham…®n ovavim. 
\p  
\v 2 Abraham Aisak…®n afeziam. Ez…® Aisak, Jekop…®n afeziam. Ez…® Jekop Juda ko an aveghbuabar afeziam.\f + \fr 1:2 \ft Juda uan aveghbuaba ko, me Israel…®n anabar 12plan inaziba.\f* 
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Jenesis 38:29-30; Rut 4:18-22\x*Ez…® Juda, Peres ko Seran afeziam. Aning…®n amebam Tamar. Ez…® Peres Hesron…®n afeziam, Ez…® Hesron, Ram…®n afeziam.  
\v 4 Ez…® Ram Aminadap…®n afeziam, Ez…® Aminadap Nason…®n afeziam, ez…® Nason Salmon…®n afeziam.  
\v 5 Ez…® Salmon Boas…®n afeziam. An amebam Rahap. Ez…® Boas Obet…®n afeziam, an amebam Rut. Ez…® Obet Jesin afeziam, Ez…® Jesi Atrivim Devit…®n afeziam. 
\p  
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt 2 Samuel 12:24\x*Ez…® Devit Solomon…®n afeziam, an amebam Urian amuim.\f + \fr 1:6 \ft Amizir ziar kagh otiviziba, Israelian amiziba puvat…®. Me Israel…®n gumazibar iti. Tamar ko Rahap aning Kenan…®n amizimning. Rut, a Moap…®n amizim. Batseba Solomon…®n amebam, a uab…®ra Israel…®n amizim. A faragha Urian ike, Uria Hitit…®n gumazim.\f* 
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt 1 Eghaghaniba 3:10-16\x*Ez…® Solomon Rehoboam…®n afeziam. Ez…® Rehoboam Abiyan afeziam, Ez…® Abiya Asan afeziam.  
\v 8 Ez…® Asa Jehosafat…®n afeziam. Ez…® Jehosafat Jehoram…®n afeziam. Ez…® Jehoram Usian afeziam.  
\v 9 Ez…® Usia Jotam…®n afeziam. Ez…® Jotam Ahas…®n afeziam. Ez…® Ahas Hesekian afeziam.  
\v 10 Ez…® Hesekia Manasen afeziam. Ez…® Manase Emon…®n afeziam. Ez…® Emon Josaian afeziam.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt 2 Atriviba 24:14-15; 1 Eghaghaniba 3:15; 2 Eghaghaniba 36:10; Jeremaia 27:20\x*Ez…® Josaia Jehoiakin ko an aveghbuar mabar afeziam. Dughiar kam…®n Israelia ghua kalabuziar gumazamizibar m…®n Babilon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghue. 
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt Esra 3:2\x*Ez…® me Babilon…®n kalabus…®n ghuez…®, g…®n Jehoiakin Sealtiel…®n afeziam. Ez…® Sealtiel Serubabel…®n afeziam.  
\v 13 Ez…® Serubabel Abiut…®n afeziam. Ez…® Abiut Eliakim…®n afeziam. Ez…® Eliakim Asor…®n afeziam.  
\v 14 Ez…® Asor Sadok…®n afeziam. Ez…® Sadok Akim…®n afeziam. Ez…® Akim Eliut…®n afeziam.  
\v 15 Ez…® Eliut Eleasar…®n afeziam. Ez…® Eleasar Matan…®n afeziam. Ez…® Matan Jekop…®n afeziam.  
\v 16 Ez…® Jekop Josep…®n afeziam, a Marian pam. 
\p Ez…® Maria Iesus bate, ez…® me ziar kam Krais a gat…®. A Gumazir God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezim. 
\p  
\v 17 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Abraham…®n dughiam…®n ikegha ghua Atrivim Devit…®n dughiam…®n tu, 14plan ovaviba otifi. Ez…® Devit…®n dughiam…®n ikegha ghua dughiar Israelia Babilon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n kalabuziabar m…®n ikezim, 14plan ovaviba otifi. Ez…® dughiar me kalabuziabar m…®n ikezim…®n ikegha ghua God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim, Krais…®n dughiam…®n tuzim, uaghan 14plan ovaviba otifi. 
\s1 Maria Krais Iesus bate, a God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim 
\r (Luk 2:1-7) 
\p  
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt Luk 1:27; 1:35\x*Krais Iesus otozir eghaghanimra kara, a God Uam e Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim. An amebam Maria, me Josep…®n ikiasa a ginaba. Egha aning t…®ghar uaning inigh ikiasava amima, Maria navim asangi. God…®n Duamra borim a gat…®.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt God…®n Araziba 24:1\x*Ez…® Josep God…®n damazim derazir gumazim an averara Maria atagh…®raghasa n…®ghn…®si. An azenan Maria aghums…®zim a dan…®ngan aghua.  
\v 20 Egha a kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gha itima Ekiam…®n ensel…®n mam irebam…®n kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúJosep, n…® Devit…®n ovavim, n…® atiatingan mark…®. N…® Maria inigh an ik…®. A navim asangizir borim, a God…®n Duam da ize.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 1:21 \xt Luk 1:31; 2:21; Aposel 4:12; 13:23; 13:38\x*An otarim bateght…®ma, eght…® a uan gumazamizibar arazir kuraba g…®n amadagh men akurvagham. Kamagh…®n n…® ziam Iesus a dat…®gh.‚Äù\f + \fr 1:21 \ft Ziam Iesus Hibrun akam…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam ko magh ghu, ‚ÄúEkiam, a gumazamiziba ua me iniamin gumazim.‚Äù Ziam Iesus Grigh…®n akam. Me Hibrun akam…®n ziam, ‚ÄúJosua,‚Äù Iesus gar…®si.\f* 
\p  
\v 22 Arazir kaba kamagh…®n otiva, egha God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am…®n m…®raram otifi.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 1:23 \xt Aisaia 7:14\x*A kamagh…®n m…®keme: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúAmizir gumazitam ko akuizir puvat…®zim navim asegh, otaritam bategham. 
\q2 Eght…® me ziar kam Emanuel a dar…®gham, ziar kam…®n m…®ngarim kara, ‚ÄòGod e ko iti.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\b  
\m  
\v 24 Ez…® Josep daguraguim…®n d…®kavigha, Ekiam…®n ensel irebam…®n aven a m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, ghua Maria inigha an iti.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 1:25 \xt Luk 2:7; 2:21\x*A poroghamiba uari isava akuir arazitam Maria gamizir puvat…®gha, ghua dughiar an otarim batezim. Ez…® a ziam Iesus isa a gat…®. 
\c 2  
\s1 Saghon itir fofozir gumaziba Iesus bagha ize 
\p  
\v 1 Maria Distrik Judian aven itir nguibam Betlehem…®n Iesus bate. Dughiar kam…®n Herot, Atrivim…®n iti. Amebam Iesus batez…®ma fofozir gumazir maba aruem anadi nagh…®n ikegha Jerusalem…®n ize.\f + \fr 2:1 \ft Atrivim Herot Judian Distrik ko Judian borogh…®n itir distrighbar gari. Herot Atrivim…®n ikia, uaghan Rom…®n Atrivir Ekiam Sisar…®n apem…®n iti.\f* 
\v 2 \x - \xo 2:2 \xt D…®boboniba 24:17\x*Egha me kamagh…®n azai, ‚ÄúBorir Judabar Atrivim…®n ikiamim, amebam a batez…® a managh iti? E an gun m…®geir m…®kovezim aruem anadi nagh…®n an ganigha an ziam fasa izi.‚Äù  
\v 3 Ez…® Herot akar kam baregha an d…®ghorim a b…®ra. Ez…® Jerusalem…®n itir darazi uaghan kamagh…®n ami.  
\v 4 Egha Herot ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba ko Judan Arazibagh fozir gumazibar diagha me akuvagha kamagh…®n men azai, ‚ÄúGod Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim, an amebam managh a batam?‚Äù  
\v 5 Ez…® me ghaze, ‚ÄúJudian Distrigh…®n aven itir nguibam Betlehem…®n, an amebam a batam. E bizir kam kamagh…®n a g…®fo, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim…®n osizirim kamagh…®n iti: 
\b  
\q1  
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt Maika 5:2; Jon 7:42\x*‚Äú‚Äâ‚ÄòN…® Betlehem, n…® Judan nguazim…®n aven iti. 
\q1 N…® Judabar nguibar ekiabar tong…®n uaghan ziam iti, 
\q3 n…®n aven gumazitam na bagh gumazir dapanim…®n otogh 
\q4 Israelia gativagh men ganam.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® Herot averara aruem anadi nagh…®n izezir gumazibar diagha m…®kovezim otozir dughiam bagha men azai. A me faraghav…®ra m…®kovezim…®n apizir dughiam g…®fogha,  
\v 8 egha me isa Betlehem…®n me amadagha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa mang…® borim bativs…® deraghv…®ra rui. Ia a batogh…®va ua na bagh m…®g…®r…®g…®am amadagh. Eght…® k…® uaghan mang…®, an ziam fam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 9 Me Herot baregha zuima m…®kovezir me faragha aruem anadi nagh…®n ganizim, men faragha ghua borim itir danganim batogha a gis…®rara iti.\f + \fr 2:9 \ft Betlehem a Jerusalem…®n saghon itir puvat…®. Aning t…®zim 8 kilomitan iti.\f* 
\v 10 Me m…®kovezim…®n ganigha bar akonge. 
\p  
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Onger Akaba 72:10; Aisaia 60:6\x*Egha me d…®penim…®n aven ghua borim uan amebam Maria ko, aning bato. Me tevibar p…®righa avigha ghuaghira borim…®n ziam fe. Egha me uan m…®tariba kuigha bizir aghuir a bagha inigha izezibar an ekarim gami. Me gol ko mughuriar aghuim itir borem ko avir m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim gamim da isava a gan…®ngi. 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® God irebam…®n me batogha Herot bagh ua mangan me anogoroke. Ez…® me tuavir igharazim…®n uamategha uan nguibam…®n ghue. 
\s1 Josep ko Maria borim inigha Isip…®n zui 
\p  
\v 13 Fofozir gumaziba ghuez…®ma Ekiam…®n ensel…®n mam irebam…®n Josep batogha a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® d…®kavigh borim iniva an amebam sara inigh…®va ia ar…® Isip…®n mang…®. Herot borim bagh ruiva am…®sueght…® an aremeghasa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia mang…® magh…®ra ik…® mang…®t…®, dughiar k…® ua n…® m…®k…®mamim.‚Äù  
\v 14 Ez…®ma Josep d…®kavigha borim isa an amebam inigha me d…®magarir kamra Isip…®n ghue.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt Hosea 11:1\x*Egha Josep Isip…®n ikia ghua, dughiar Herot ovengezim. Arazir kabanagh otiva Ekiam…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam…®n akatorim…®n m…®kemezir m…®g…®r…®g…®abar m…®n otifi. A kamagh…®n m…®keme, ‚ÄúNan Otarim Isip…®n kantrin itima, k…® an diaz…®ma an azenan ize.‚Äù 
\s1 Atrivim Herot m…®kemez…®ma, me borir av…®ribav soghez…®ma da ariaghire 
\p  
\v 16 Ez…® Herot garima, fofozir gumazir aruem anadi nagh…®n izeziba a gifara. Ez…® Herot bar puv atara uan m…®dorozir gumaziba amadagha, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar gavgavim me gan…®ga, me amadima me ghua, Betlehem koma an borogh…®n itir nguibaba bar dar ghua otarir azenir pumuning ko an apengan itiba, me m…®sozima me ariaghire. Kar ana aruem anadi nagh…®n izezir fofozir gumazibar m…®g…®r…®g…®am…®n g…®n ghua kamagh…®n ami.  
\v 17 Arazir kabanagh otiva God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Jeremaia m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, otifi. A ghaze: 
\b  
\q1  
\v 18 \x - \xo 2:18 \xt Jenesis 35:19; Jeremaia 31:15\x*‚ÄúMe Raman nguibam…®n tiarir mam barasi, azirakam ko tuatem. 
\q2 Resel…®n boriba ua itir puvat…®. 
\q1 Kamagh…®ra a uan ovengezir boriba bagha azi. 
\q2 A navir am…®rizim inian aghua.‚Äù 
\s1 Josep uan amuim ko Iesus inigha uamategha uan nguibam…®n ize 
\p  
\v 19 Herot ovengez…®ma, Josep Isip…®n itima, Ekiam…®n ensel irebam…®n Josep bato.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 2:20 \xt Ua Me Ini 4:19\x*Egha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúBorim m…®soghasa amir darazi me ovenge. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® d…®kavigh borim koma an amebam inigh ua Israel…®n mang…®.‚Äù  
\v 21 Ez…® a d…®kavigha borim isa an amebam inigha me ua Israel…®n ghue. 
\p  
\v 22 Egha an orazima, Arkelaus uan afeziam Herot…®n danganim inigha Judian Atrivim…®n iti. Ez…® Josep Judian Distrigh…®n mangan atiatingi. Egha God da irebam…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am inigha Galilin Distrigh…®n ghu.\f + \fr 2:22 \ft Atrivim Herot ovengez…®ma Rom…®n gavman a garir kantri ab…®gha an otaribagh an…®ngi. Ez…® Arkelaus atrivim…®n ikia Distrik Galili ko Distrik Judian gari. A 10plan azenibar atrivim…®n ike.\f* 
\v 23 \x - \xo 2:23 \xt Mak 1:24; Luk 2:39; Jon 1:45\x*A ghua Galilin Distrigh…®n nguibar mam, Nasaret…®n apera. Bizir kaba otiva God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim m…®kemez…® mogh…®n otifi, a ghaze, ‚ÄúMe Nasaretian Gumazim, a dar…®gham.‚Äù 
\c 3  
\s1 Jon, Gumazamiziba Ruer Gumazim, akam akuri 
\r (Mak 1:2-8; Luk 3:1-18; Jon 1:19-28) 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Mak 1:4; 1:15; Luk 3:2-3; Jon 1:28\x*Dughiar kamnagh…®n Gumazamiziba Ruer Gumazim Jon izava, Judian gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ikia akam akuri.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt Matyu 4:17; Mak 1:15\x*Egha ghaze, ‚ÄúGod Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam, a rogh…®ra ize. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia navibagh iragh.‚Äù\f + \fr 3:2 \ft Ziar kamning, ‚ÄúKingdom Bilong God,‚Äù ko ‚ÄúKingdom Bilong Heven,‚Äù aning God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam m…®gei. Ez…® kagh Matyu osiriz…® Akar Aghuim…®n aven e ghaze, ‚ÄúGod Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam.‚Äù\f* 
\p  
\v 3 \x - \xo 3:3 \xt Aisaia 40:3; Mak 1:3; Luk 1:76; Jon 1:23\x*God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Aisaia fom…®ra Jon…®n gun m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir tiarir mam gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n d…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòIa Ekiam bagh tuaviba azen…®va, dar k…®r.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 \x - \xo 3:4 \xt 1 Samuel 14:25-26; Sekaraia 13:4; Mak 1:6\x*Jon an as…®zim kamel…®n ar…®zibar ingarizir iniba ikegha as…®zir inim uan ivariam ike. A inir kaba ikeghava odeziba ko ruarim…®n haniba api.\f + \fr 3:4 \ft Jon apir dagheba ko an azuir korotiaba an akakagha ghaze, a God…®n akam inigha izezir gumazim Elaijan m…®n iti. N…® akar 2 Atriviba 1:8…®n itim…®n gan.\f* 
\v 5 Ez…® gumazamiziba, me Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam ko Judian Distrik ko Jordan…®n danganim…®n ikegha, bar a bagha izava,  
\v 6 uan arazir kurabar gun m…®geima a Jordan…®n Fanem…®n me rue. 
\p  
\v 7 \x - \xo 3:7 \xt Matyu 12:34; 23:33; Luk 3:7; Rom 5:9; 1 Tesalonika 1:10\x*Egha a garima, Farisiba ko Sadyusibar av…®rim, a gumazamiziba ruer danganim…®n izi. Ez…® a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa kuruzir divir anababa, tina ia m…®kemez…®, ia God…®n an…®ngagharir g…®n izamim…®n ar…® mangasa?  
\v 8 Ia navim g…®razir arazibar amu.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 3:9 \xt Jon 8:33; Aposel 13:26; Rom 2:28-29; 4:1; 4:11-12; 4:16\x*Egh ia pura uarigh n…®ghn…®gh suam ‚ÄòE Abraham…®n ovaviba.‚Äô K…® ia m…®gei, God dag…®ar kabara amight…® da Abraham…®n ovavibar m…®n otivighamin gavgavim iti.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 3:10 \xt Matyu 7:19; Luk 13:6-9; Jon 15:6\x*Sobiam dat…®r…®gh…®n temer povibar iti, eght…® temer dagher ov…®zir aghuiba itir puvat…®ziba, God bar da okegh…®va da is…®va avim m…®k…®nam. 
\p  
\v 11 \x - \xo 3:11 \xt Aisaia 4:4; Malakai 3:2; Jon 1:26-27; 1:33; Aposel 1:5; 2:3-4; 1 Korin 12:13\x*‚ÄúIa navibagh irazir arazim akakaghasa k…® d…®pam…®n ia rue. Ez…® nan g…®n izir gumazim, an gavgavim nan gavgavim gafira. Ez…® k…® an dagarir asuabar ateramin gavgaviba puvat…®. Gumazir kam God…®n Duam ko avim…®n ia ruam.  
