\v 17 \x - \xo 10:17 \xt Matyu 24:9\x*\x - \xo 10:17-20 \xt Mak 13:9-11; Luk 12:11-12; 21:12-15\x*Ia deraghv…®ra uari bagh gan. Me ian suiragh, uan kaunselbar damazibar ia is…® kotiam dar…®gh…®va, egh me uan God ko m…®geir d…®penibar ia fozorogham.  
