\p  
\v 21 \x - \xo 10:21 \xt Maika 7:6; Matyu 10:35; Luk 21:16\x*‚ÄúAveghbuaba uarira uari is…® apanibar an…®ngt…® me me m…®soght…® me ar…®m…®ghiram. Eght…® afeziaba uan boriba uaghan kamagh…®ra me damuam. Boriba uan ameboghfeziabar akaba batogh…®va ovengamin arazibar me damut…®, me ar…®m…®ghiram.  
