\v 6 \x - \xo 11:6 \xt Matyu 13:57; 26:31\x*Gumazamizir nan ganigha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan itiba, men n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ik…®v…®ra ik…®, eght…® men navir averiaba deraght…® me bar akuegham!‚Äù 
