\v 3 \x - \xo 18:3 \xt Matyu 19:14; Mak 10:15; Luk 18:17\x*Egha a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ia uari giragh borir dozir kabar m…®n otoghan kogh, ia God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven ikian kogham.  
