\v 5 \x - \xo 18:5 \xt Matyu 10:40-42; Luk 9:48; 10:16; Jon 13:20\x*Egh gumazitam o amizitam na g…®n…®ghn…®gh egh borir dozir kamagh garitam inigh an akuragham, kamagh…®n a na inigha nan akurvasi.‚Äù 
