\v 10-11 \x - \xo 18:10-11 \xt Jenesis 48:16; Onger Akaba 34:7; Luk 19:10; Jon 3:17; 12:47; Hibru 1:14\x*‚ÄúIa deragh uari bagh gan! Ia borir dozir kabar tong…®n tav g…®n…®ghn…®gh kamagh…®n m…®k…®man mark…®, a pura bizim.\f + \fr 18:10-11 \ft Akar faraghav…®ra itim…®n, Grigh…®n akam ghaze, ‚Äúborir dozir kaba.‚Äù Akar otevir kam uaghan, ves 6 ko ves 14…®n iti. Akar kam Matyu 10:42, uaghan an iti, egha ghaze, ‚ÄúSuren gumazir ziaba puvat…®ziba.‚Äù Iesus ti boribara m…®geir puvat…®, a uaghan uan suren gumazir igharazibav gei.\f* Puvat…®. K…® ia m…®gei, men enselba zurara nan Afeziar uan Nguibam…®n itim…®n damazim…®n iti.‚Äù\f + \fr 18:10-11 \ft Akar abuananam…®n, fofozir gumazir maba ghaze, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevir mam uaghan vez…®n kam…®n iti. Akar kam ghaze, ‚ÄúE fo, Gumazamizibar Otarim gumazamizir tuavim ataghiziba iniasa ize.‚Äù\f* 
