\v 15 \x - \xo 18:15 \xt Ofa Gami 19:17; Luk 17:3; Galesia 6:1; Jems 5:19-20; 1 Pita 4:8\x*Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…®n aveghbuam arazir kuram n…® damight…®, n…® an bighan mang…® egh gua uaningra ik…®va n…® a ko gua bizir kam anek…®righ. A n…® baraght…®, n…® ua uan aveghbuam inigham.\f + \fr 18:15 \ft Vez…®n kam…®n itir m…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevim, ‚Äún…® damight…®ma,‚Äù fofozir gumazir maba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, gumazir ti igharazim an osiri. Matyu uab…® puvat…®.\f* 
\v 16 \x - \xo 18:16 \xt God…®n Araziba 19:15; Jon 8:17; 2 Korin 13:1; 1 Timoti 5:19\x*Egh a n…® baraghan aghuaght…®, n…® gumazitam uam, o igharazir pumuning uam me inight…®, me n…®n g…®n mang…®. E fo, God…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® gumazitam…®n arazir kuram an gun a m…®k…®ms…®, gumazir pumuning ko m…®kezim gavgavim n…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®abar an…®ngam.‚Äô  
