\v 20 \x - \xo 18:20 \xt Matyu 28:20; Jon 14:23\x*Egh gumazir pumuning, o pumuning ko m…®kezim nan ziam…®n uari akuvagh ik…®t…®, k…® uab…® men tong…®n ikiam.‚Äù 
