\v 34 \x - \xo 18:34 \xt Matyu 5:25-26\x*Egha atrivim atarava gumazir kam isa, m…®zazim a gasamin gumazibar dafarim gat…®. Eght…® a kagh…®ra ik…® mang…®, a biziba bar da ikarvaghamin dughiam…®n tugham. 
