\v 35 \x - \xo 18:35 \xt Matyu 6:12-15; Mak 11:25-26; Efesus 4:32; Kolosi 3:13; Jems 2:13\x*‚ÄúEght…® ia uan aveghbuabar arazir kurar me ia gamiba, ia guizbang…®ra uan navir averiabar aven, da g…®n amangan koght…®ma, nan Afeziar uan Nguibam…®n itim uaghan kamagh…®ra ia damuam.‚Äù 
