\c 23  
\s1 Farisiba ko Judan Arazibagh fozir gumaziba arazir kurabagh ami 
\r (Mak 12:38-39; Luk 11:43; 11:46; 20:45-46) 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Iesus g…®n gumazamizir av…®riba ko an suren gumazibagh eghari.  
\v 2 Egha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúJudan Arazibagh fozir gumaziba ko Farisiba, me Moses…®n danganim inigha Moses Osirizir Araziba ia geghari.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 23:3 \xt Malakai 2:7-8\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me ia m…®geir akaba, ia da baragha dagh eghari mogh…®n dar amu. Egh me amir araziba, ia men g…®n mang…® dar amuan mark…®. Me m…®g…®r…®g…®ar bar av…®ribagh amua egha uari dar g…®n zuir puvat…®.  
\v 4 Me kamagh…®n amua, mati me bizir bar os…®mt…®ziba isava gumazamizibar d…®p…®zibagh is…®n ar…®zima, me da ateran buraghburasi. Egha me tong uan dafar puzitam…®n men akurvaghan n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 5 \x - \xo 23:5 \xt Matyu 6:1\x*‚ÄúArazir me amiba, me uarir ganasa oda dagh ami. Me God…®n Akar maba, uan daveriaba ko guaghaf…®vibar da osirigha, egha dagh amiz…®, da bar ekefe, ez…® me da azui. Egha korotiar ap…®nibar itir dueviar bar ruariba, me da azui. Egha ghaze, e arazir kam…®n uari akakagh suam, e guizbang…®ra God…®n akabar g…®n zui.\f + \fr 23:5 \ft God ko m…®geir daveriaba, kar Judaba ak…®nafarir dozibar God…®n akar maba osiri, egha da isa m…®tarir nguzir mabagh aghui. Egha da isava uan agharir k…®riabagh aghui, egha maba isa uan guabagh afe. N…® Ua Me Ini 13:9 ko 13:16 ko God…®n Araziba 6:8 ko 11:18, dar gan. Judaba uaghan Ak…®nafarim D…®boboniba 15:37-41…®n garava sazir oteviba uan korotiabagh itui. Iesus Judan Arazibagh fozir gumaziba ko Farisiba me m…®g…®a g…®a ghaze, me daveriar ekiaba aghuigha, egha sazir ruariba azui, egha uari akakagha ghaze, e guizbang…®ra God…®n akabar g…®n zui. Kar me uarir ganasa odava arazir kabagh ami.\f* 
\v 6 \x - \xo 23:6 \xt Matyu 6:5; Mak 12:38-39; Luk 11:43; 14:7\x*Egha isar ekiabar me danganir ziaba itiba isava, God ko m…®geir d…®penibar aven dabirabir aghuaribagh apiaghiri.  
\v 7 Egh me maket…®n danganibar mang…®t…®, gumazamiziba ‚ÄòTisaba‚Äô me dar…®gh, men ziaba fasa me bar akonge. 
\p  
\v 8 ‚ÄúK…® ghaze, gumazitam ia ‚ÄòTisa‚Äô a dar…®ghan mark…®. Bar mark…®. Ian tisan bar vam…®ra, ia bar aveghdiariba.  
\v 9 Egh ia nguazim…®n kagh gumazitam ‚ÄòAfeziam‚Äô a dar…®ghan mark…®. Ian Afeziar bar vam…®ra, a uan Nguibam…®n iti.  
\v 10 Egh me ‚ÄòGumazir Dapanim‚Äô ian tav dar…®ghan mark…®. Ian Gumazir Dapanir vam…®ra iti, a Gumazir God Uam E Iniasa M…®sevezim.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 23:11 \xt Matyu 20:26-27; Mak 9:35; 10:43-44; Luk 22:26\x*Ian gumazamizir ekiaba pura ian ingangarir gumazamizibar m…®n ik…®.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 23:12 \xt Jop 22:29; Aghuzir Akaba 15:33; 29:23; Esekiel 21:26; Luk 14:11; 18:14; Jems 4:6; 1 Pita 5:5\x*Gumazamizir uan ziaba feba, God me ab…®nam. Eght…® gumazamizir uari ab…®riba, God me feght…® me ziar ekiaba iniam.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus Judan Arazibagh fozir gumaziba ko Farisibar arazir kurabar gun me m…®gei 
\r (Mak 12:40; Luk 11:39-52; 20:47) 
\p  
\v 13-14 \x - \xo 23:13-14 \xt Luk 11:52\x*Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Judan Arazibagh fozir gumaziba ko Farisiba, Iavzika, ia bar ikuvigham! Ia ifavaribagh amir gumaziba! Ia God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n tiam asaraz…®, gumazamiziba azenan iti. Egha ia uaghan aven mangan aghua. Ez…® gumazamiziba aven mangasava amima ia men tuaviba ap…®ri.\f + \fr 23:13-14 \ft Fofozir gumazir maba ghaze, akar kamnagh uaghan kagh ikiam. A kamak…®n, ‚ÄúIa Judan Arazibagh fozir gumaziba ko Farisiba, Iavzika. Ia gumazir m…®zer pumuning itiba, ia amizir paba ovengezibagh ifara men d…®penibar ok…®a, oda m…®g…®r…®g…®ar bar ruariba God ko dagh ami. Kotiam…®n Dughiam…®n ia bar ikuvigham.‚Äù N…® Mak 12:40…®n gan.\f* 
\p  
\v 15 ‚ÄúIa Judan Arazibagh fozir gumaziba ko Farisiba, Iavzika! Ia bar ikuvigham! Ia ifavaribagh amir gumaziba! Ia ongariba ko nguazir igharaziba bar dar ghua, suren gumazir vam…®ra iniasa ruiagha arui. Eght…® ia gumazitam batogh Judan Arazibar a geghant…®, a ian n…®ghn…®zibar g…®n mang…®, egh a bar ian m…®rara uaghan hel…®n mangam. Ia a damight…®, a bar ia gafiragh arazir kurabar amuam. 
\p  
\v 16 \x - \xo 23:16 \xt Matyu 5:33-34; 15:14\x*‚ÄúIa damazir okav…®r…®ziba, egha ia gumazir igharaziba tuavim men akakaghasa! Iavzika, ia bar ikuvigham! Ia kamagh…®n gumazamizibar sure gamua ghaze, ‚ÄòGumazir manam guiz…®n m…®k…®ms…®va, God…®n D…®penim…®n akakagh m…®k…®mt…®, an araziba pura bizim. Egh gumazir kam guiz…®n m…®k…®ms…®, gol…®n God…®n D…®penim…®n aven itibar akakagh m…®k…®mt…®, kar a guizbang…®ra m…®gei, egh a m…®kemezir arazim…®n g…®n mang…®, a damu.‚Äô  
\v 17 Ia gumazir onganir damazir okav…®r…®ziba, tizim God…®n damazim…®n ekefe? Ti gol, o ti God…®n D…®penim? Ia fo, gol…®n kam God…®n D…®penim…®n aven iti, egha tuavir kam…®n gol…®n kam God…®n bizim…®n oto.  
\v 18 Egha ia uaghan kamagh…®n men sure gamua ghaze, ‚ÄòGumazitam uan m…®g…®r…®g…®aba gavgavim dar an…®ngs…®, ofa gamir dakozim…®n akakaght…®, an m…®g…®r…®g…®aba pura biziba. Eght…® gumazim ofa gamir dakozim…®n itir ofabar akakagh m…®k…®mt…®, kar a guizbang…®ra m…®gei, egh a m…®kemezir m…®g…®r…®g…®abar g…®n mang…®.‚Äô  
\v 19 Ia damazir okav…®r…®ziba, bizir manam God…®n damazim…®n ekefe, ti ofa gamir dakozim…®n itir ofaba, o ofa gamir dakozim uab…®? Ia fo, ofaba ofa gamir dakozim…®n iti, egha tuavir kam…®n ofan kam God…®n bizim…®n oto.  
\v 20 Eght…® gumazim uan m…®g…®r…®g…®aba gavgavim dar an…®ngs…®, ofa gamir dakozim…®n akakagh m…®k…®mt…®, an m…®g…®r…®g…®aba ofa gamir dakozim ko ofa gamir dakozim…®n itir ofaba uaghara aning…®n akakasi.  
\v 21 Egh gumazim uan m…®g…®r…®g…®aba gavgavim dar an…®ngs…® God…®n D…®penim…®n akakagh m…®k…®mt…®, an m…®g…®r…®g…®aba God…®n D…®penim, ko God…®n uan D…®penim…®n aven itim, v…®rara aning…®n akakasi.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 23:22 \xt Aisaia 66:1; Matyu 5:34\x*Eght…® gumazitam uan m…®g…®r…®g…®aba gavgavim dar an…®ngs…®, God…®n Nguibam…®n akakagh m…®k…®mt…®, an m…®g…®r…®g…®aba God…®n atrivir dabirabim, ko God…®n uan atrivir dabirabim gaperazim, uaghara aning…®n akakasi. 
\p  
\v 23 \x - \xo 23:23 \xt Ofa Gami 27:30; Hosea 6:6; Maika 6:8; Luk 11:42\x*‚ÄúIa Judan Arazibagh fozir gumaziba ko Farisiba, Iavzika, ia bar ikuvigham! Ia ifavaribagh amir gumaziba! Ia is…®ngt…®zim daghebagh an…®dir zuravarir 10plan pozibar da ar…®gha, egha dar pozir vam…®ra God gan…®di. Egha Moses Osirizir Arazibar aven itir arazir ekiaba atagh…®rasi. Ia, God…®n guiz…®n arazim, ko apangkuvir arazim, ko n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n itir arazim, ia da g…®n amadi. Ia faragh arazir ekiar kabar g…®n mang…® dar amu, egh uaghan arazir dozir ia amiba sara, uaghan dar amu.  
\v 24 Ia damazir okav…®r…®ziba, egha gumazir igharaziba tuavim men akakaghasa! Ia mati, gumazim sibaba d…®pars…®zim…®n itima, a bar derav…®ra gara da isa da makuri. Ez…® as…®zir ekiam kamel, a d…®pars…®zim…®n aven itima, an an garir puvat…®gha, a tui. 
\p  
\v 25 \x - \xo 23:25 \xt Mak 7:4\x*‚ÄúIa Judan Arazibagh fozir gumaziba ko Farisiba, Iavzika! Ia bar ikuvigham! Ia ifavaribagh amir gumaziba! Ia bar deraghav…®ra kapba ko itaribar azeniba rue, ez…® dar aven itir dagher kaba bar iz…®fa. Ia, ok…®mak…®ar araziba ko uarira uarigh n…®ghn…®zir arazibar tuavim…®n, dagher kaba ini.  
\v 26 Ia Farisiba, ian damaziba okafi! Ia faragh…®v…®ra kapbar averiaba ruegh, eght…® dar ot…®gh…®naba uaghan zuegham. 
\p  
\v 27 \x - \xo 23:27 \xt Luk 11:44; Aposel 23:3\x*‚ÄúIa Judan Arazibagh fozir gumaziba ko Farisiba, Iavzika! Ia bar ikuvigham. Ia ifavaribagh amir gumaziba! Ia mati, me matmatiam pen…®n ghurghurim a gaghui, ez…® matmatiam…®n ganganim azenan bar dera. Ez…® an aven gumazir kuabar aghariba ko bizir kuriba bar iz…®fa.  
\v 28 \x - \xo 23:28 \xt Luk 16:15\x*Ia uaghan kamagh…®n iti. Me azenan ian gara ghaze, ia gumazir aghuiba. Ez…® ifavarir araziba ko arazir bar kuraba, guizbang…®ra ian navir averiabagh iz…®fa.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 29 Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Judan Arazibagh fozir gumaziba ko Farisiba, Iavzika! Ia bar ikuvigham! Ia ifavaribagh amir gumaziba! Ia, fom…®ra itir God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba, men moziba deraghv…®ra dar k…®rm…®gha, egha gumazir arazir aghuibagh amizibar moziba deraghav…®ra dar adiaribagh ami.  
\v 30 Egha kamagh uariv gei, ‚ÄòE ti uan inazibar dughiam…®n ikia, egha ti men akuragha God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibav soghezir puvat…®ghai.‚Äô  
\v 31 \x - \xo 23:31 \xt Aposel 7:52\x*Ia kamagh m…®g…®a uari akakagha ghaze, ‚ÄòE God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibav soghezir gumazibar boriba!‚Äô  
\v 32 Aria, mang…®, ia uan inaziba amua taghizir arazir kuraba, bar da g…®fagh! 
\p  
\v 33 \x - \xo 23:33 \xt Matyu 3:7; 12:34; Luk 3:7\x*‚ÄúIa kuruziba! Ia dab…®r…®zir anababa! God uan kot…®n aven ian araziba tuis…®gh…®va, ia is…® hel…®n avir ekiam…®n ia amangam! Ia man tuavitam…®n mang…®, hel…®n avim gitagham? Bar puvat…®gham! 
\p  
\v 34 \x - \xo 23:34 \xt Matyu 10:23; 1 Tesalonika 2:15\x*‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®, ia oragh, k…® ia bagha God…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba, ko gumazir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba itiba, ko God…®n Arazibagh fozir gumaziba, me amangam. Eght…® ia men taraziv soght…® me ar…®m…®ghiram, egh tarazi is…® ter ighuvibar me afughafugham, egh tarazi ian God ko m…®geir d…®penibar aven benibar me fozorogham. Egh ia uan nguibar ekiabar me batogh men g…®nt…®ght…®, me ar…® nguibar igharazibar mangam.  
\v 35 \x - \xo 23:35 \xt Jenesis 4:8; 2 Eghaghaniba 24:20-21; Hibru 11:4\x*Eght…® arazir aghuibagh amir gumazamiziba bar, me m…®soghezir gumazibar ivezir kuram, ia a iniam. Gumazir aghuibav sozir arazir kam, gumazir aghuim Abel…®n dughiam…®n ikegha, iza Berekian otarim Sekaraian dughiam…®n tu. Gumazir kam, ia God…®n D…®penim ko ofa gamir dakozim t…®zim…®n ia a m…®soghez…® an areme, ez…® iarara ivezir kuram uan arazir kuram bagh a iniam.  
\v 36 K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, arazir kurar kabar ivezir kuram, a dat…®r…®gh…®n itir gumazamiziba me bativam.‚Äù 
