\v 37 \x - \xo 23:37 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 24:21; Onger Akaba 17:8; 91:4; Aposel 7:59; 1 Tesalonika 2:15\x*Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúOio, ia Jerusalem…®n adarasi, k…® ian apangkufi! Ia God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibav sozi me ariaghiri, egha God ia bagha amadir gumaziba, ia dag…®aba isa, me ginivi, me ariaghiri. Dughiar av…®ribar k…® ian boriba akuv me mughasa, mati tuarir amebam uan av…®ziming…®n nguziba avaraz…® mogh…®n, k…® ia damuasa ifonge. Ez…® ia na bagh izan aghua.  
