\v 1 Egha Iesus God…®n D…®penim…®n m…®riam ategha azenan zuima, an suren gumaziba a bagha izi. Egha me God…®n D…®penim an akakasi.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 24:2 \xt Jeremaia 26:18; Maika 3:12; Luk 19:44\x*Ez…® an akar kam…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa D…®penim…®n itir bizir aghuir kabar gari? K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, dag…®ar kaba, gumaziba bar da pueght…® da bar mogh…®ra dagh iregham. Eght…® tam tam gis…®n ikeghan kogham.‚Äù\f + \fr 24:2 \ft Kar Matyu osirizir Iesus…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar ruarir abuananam. (4pla faragha g…®fa.) Akar kaba, da 24:2--25:46…®n iti. Da nguazim g…®vamin dughiam…®n arazibar gun m…®gei.\f* 
\s1 Iesus ghaze, os…®mt…®zir av…®riba  // g…®n otivam 
\r (Mak 13:3-13; Luk 21:7-19) 
\p  
\v 3 \x - \xo 24:3 \xt Matyu 24:27; 24:37-39; Mak 13:3-4; 1 Tesalonika 5:1\x*Egha Iesus ghua Oliv…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n aperaghav itima, an suren gumaziba uarira iza kamagh…®n an azai, ‚ÄúN…® e m…®k…®m, bizir kaba dughiar manam…®n otivam? Arazir manamnagh faragh otoght…®, e fogh suam, ‚ÄòN…® ua izam,‚Äô eght…® nguazir kam uaghan g…®vam?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 Ez…® Iesus me ikaragha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa uari bagh deraghv…®ra gan, gumazitam iz…® ia gifaran mark…®.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 24:5 \xt Jeremaia 14:14; 23:21; 23:25; Matyu 24:23-24; Jon 5:43; Aposel 5:36-37; 1 Jon 2:18\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazir bar av…®riba iz…®, nan ziam is…®va uari gas…® suam, ‚ÄòK…®rara, k…® Gumazir God Gumazamiziba Ua Me Iniasa M…®sevezim.‚Äô Egh me gumazamizir av…®ribagh ifaram.  
\v 6 Eght…® ia rogh…®ra itir m…®dorozir ekiabar n…®g…®niba baragh, egh saghon itir m…®dorozir ekiabar akaba baragham. Egh ia d…®gavir kuram damuan mark…®. Arazir kaba otivam, eght…® nguazir kam g…®vamin dughiam t…®ghar izam.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 24:7 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 15:6; Aisaia 19:2; Hagai 2:22; Sekaraia 14:13; Aposel 11:28\x*Kantrin mam…®n itir darazi d…®kavigh kantrin igharazim…®n itir darazi ko m…®sogham. Eght…® atrivir mam…®n adarazi d…®kavigh atrivir igharazim…®n adarazi ko m…®sogham. Danganir mabar dagheba bar puvarat…®ght…®ma, gumazamiziba m…®tiriamra ikiam. Eght…® m…®k…®mk…®ziba uaghan otivam.  
\v 8 Os…®mt…®zir kaba mati, amizim otasa faraghav…®ra m…®zazim barazi mok…®n. 
\p  
\v 9 \x - \xo 24:9 \xt Matyu 10:22; Mak 13:9; Luk 21:12; Jon 15:18-20; Aposel 4:2-3; Akar Mogomem 2:10; 2:13\x*‚ÄúDughiar kam…®n me ian suigh…®va os…®mt…®ziba ia dar…®gh…®va ia m…®soght…®, ia ar…®m…®ghiram. Eght…® gumazamiziba bar nan ziam bang…®n ian aghuagham.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 24:10 \xt Matyu 11:6; 13:57; 2 Timoti 1:15\x*Egh dughiar kam…®n gumazamizir av…®riba, me uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir nan itim ategham. Egh paz…® uarira uarir amuva, uari is…® apanibar agharim dar…®gham.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 24:11 \xt Matyu 7:15; 24:5; 24:24; Aposel 20:29; 1 Timoti 4:1; 2 Pita 2:1; 1 Jon 4:1\x*Eght…® akar ifavarim akurir gumazir av…®riba otivigh, gumazamizir av…®ribagh ifaram.  
\v 12 Eght…® arazir kuraba bar iz…®vaght…®, kamagh…®n gumazamiziba uarigh ifongezir arazim ategham.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 24:13 \xt Matyu 10:22; Mak 13:13; Hibru 3:6; 3:14\x*Eght…® tina arazir kabar tong…®n gavgavigh ik…®, mang…® dughiar nguazir kam g…®vaghamim otoght…®, God uam a iniam.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 24:14 \xt Matyu 9:35; 10:18; 28:19; Rom 10:18; Kolosi 1:6; 1:23\x*Eght…® God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n Akar Aghuir kam, me a inigh a is…®va nguazim…®n itir ik…®ziba bar dar gumazamiziba bar me m…®k…®mt…®ma, me a baragham. Eght…®ma g…®n nguazir kam g…®vamin dughiam otivam.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus ghaze, bizir bar kuram otogham 
\r (Mak 13:14-23; Luk 21:20-24) 
\p  
\v 15 \x - \xo 24:15 \xt Daniel 9:27; 11:31; 12:11\x*Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa gant…®ma, bizir bar kurar God ifongezir puvat…®zim, God…®n D…®penim…®n aven ikiam. A ik…®t…®, God uan D…®penim ategham. Fom…®ra God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Daniel bizir kam…®n gun m…®keme. (Gumazir osizirir kam…®n garim, a deraghv…®ra n…®ghnigh egh a g…®fogh.)  
\v 16 Dughiar kam…®n Judian Distrigh…®n itir gumazamiziba ar…® m…®ghs…®abar ghuavanangam.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 24:17-18 \xt Luk 17:31\x*Egh tav d…®penim…®n p…®n itir avughsazir danganim…®n ikegh, nguazim…®n mag…®r…®, egh uam aven mang…® uan bizitam inis…® n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®.  
\v 18 Egh gumazir manam azenir ekiam…®n ikegh, egh uamategh d…®penim…®n mang…® uan azenan azuir korotiam inian mark…®.  
\v 19 Naviba adair amiziba ko boriba oteba apir amebaba, mevzika; dughiar izamin kaba bar men ikuvigham!  
\v 20 Ia amozim…®n dughiam ko Sabat…®n dughiatam…®n aran aghuagh…®va, uari bagh God ko m…®k…®m.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 24:21 \xt Daniel 9:26; 12:1; Joel 2:2; Akar Mogomem 7:14\x*Dughiar izamin kaba, da os…®mt…®zir ekiabar dughiaba. God nguazim ko overiam…®n ingarizir dughiam…®n iza dat…®r…®k…®n, egh ua kamagh…®n dughiatam otoghan kogham.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 24:22 \xt Aisaia 65:8-9; Sekaraia 14:2-3\x*Ekiam uan gumazamizir m…®sevezibagh n…®ghnigha, dughiar kurar kam…®n dughiar maba aghorez…®, da mong otefe. A ti dar aghorezir puvat…®z…®, gumazamiziba bar ariaghireghai. 
\p  
\v 23 \x - \xo 24:23 \xt Matyu 24:5; 24:11; Mak 13:21; Luk 17:23; 21:8\x*‚ÄúDughiar izamim…®n, tav ia m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòIa gan, Kraisra kara! A God Ua E Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazimra,‚Äô o, ‚ÄòIa gan, Kraisra muna!‚Äô ia an akam baraghan mark…®.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 24:24 \xt God…®n Araziba 13:1-3; Mak 13:22; 2 Tesalonika 2:8-9; Akar Mogomem 13:13-14\x*Gumazitaba iz…®va ia gifar suam, ‚ÄòK…®rara, God Gumazamiziba Ua me Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim,‚Äô o ‚Äòk…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam,‚Äô egh me mirakel…®n bar ekiaba koma d…®gavir kuram gamir arazibar amut…® da otivam. Me kamagh…®n ifonge, me gumazamiziba bar me gifaraght…®, me onganigham. Egh me gavgavim ik…®, uaghan God ua bagha m…®sevezir gumazamiziba, me uaghan me gifarasa. Kamagh…®n me mirakel…®n kabar amuam. Egh dughiataba me me gifar…®s…® damuva avegham.  
\v 25 Ia oragh! Bizir k…® faragha ia m…®kemeziba, da otivam. 
\p  
\v 26 \x - \xo 24:26-27 \xt Luk 17:23-24\x*‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®, me ia m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòIa gan. A muna gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n iti,‚Äô eght…® ia mangan mark…®. Egh me suam, ‚ÄòIa gan. A kara, d…®penir kam…®n aven modoghav iti,‚Äô ia men akam baraghan mark…®.  
\v 27 \x - \xo 24:27 \xt Matyu 24:37-39\x*Ia fo, on…®marim taghtagha, an angazangarim aruem anadi nagh…®n ikegha nguazim bar anevaragha ghua aruem ghuaghiri nagh…®n tu. Eght…® Gumazamizibar Otarim ua izamin arazim, uaghan kamagh…®ram otivt…®, nguazim…®n itir darazi bar an ganam. 
\p  
\v 28 \x - \xo 24:28 \xt Luk 17:37\x*‚ÄúGumazir kuaba iti nagh…®n, taragiaba uari akuvagham. Kamagh…®ra, Gumazamizibar Otarim iz…®t…®ma, gumazamiziba bar an ganam.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus ghaze, Gumazamizibar Otarim g…®n izam 
\r (Mak 13:24-27; Luk 21:25-28) 
\p  
\v 29 \x - \xo 24:29 \xt Aisaia 13:10; 34:4; Esekiel 32:7; Joel 2:10; 2:31; 3:15; Akar Mogomem 6:12-13\x*Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúOs…®mt…®zir ekiar kaba otivigh g…®vaght…®: 
\b  
\q1 ‚Äú‚Äâ‚ÄòAruem m…®tategham, 
\q2 eght…® iak…®nim isiraghan kogham, 
\q3 eght…® m…®koveziba overiam…®n asighiram, 
\q2 overiam…®n itir bizir gavgaviba bar uarira uari s…®vaghs…®vagh, 
\q3 uan danganiba atagh…®ragham.‚Äô 
\b  
\p  
\v 30 \x - \xo 24:30 \xt Daniel 7:13; Mak 13:26; Akar Mogomem 1:7; 6:12-13\x*‚ÄúEght…®, Gumazamizibar Otarim Izamin Dughiam, an arazarazim overiam…®n otivt…®ma, nguazim…®n itir nguibaba bar aziam. Dughiar kam…®n gumazamiziba gant…®, Gumazamizibar Otarim ghuariabagh is…®n ik…®, uan gavgavir ekiam koma angazangarir ekiam sara izam.  
\v 31 \x - \xo 24:31 \xt Aisaia 27:13; Matyu 13:41; 1 Korin 15:52; 1 Tesalonika 4:16\x*Eght…® s…®gham bar pamten arangt…®, a uan enselba ameght…®, me nguazim ko overiam…®n danganiba bar dar mang…®, a ua bagha m…®sevezir gumazamiziba akuvam, egh enselba nguazim…®n oteviba bar, me akuvagh, men aku a bagh izam.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus ghaze, ia temer figh…®n gan fogh 
\r (Mak 13:28-31; Luk 21:29-33) 
\p  
\v 32 Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúTemer figh…®n aguaba ua d…®z murt…®, ia fogh suam, amozim…®n dughiam rogh…®ra ize. Ia temer figh…®n gan n…®ghn…®zim iniam.  
\v 33 Kamagh…®ra ia bizir kabar gant…® da otivt…®, ia fogh suam, Gumazamizibar Otarim a ua izamin dughiam rogh…®ra ize. A tiar akam…®n tughav iti.  
\v 34 \x - \xo 24:34 \xt Matyu 16:28; 23:36; Mak 13:30; Luk 21:32\x*K…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei dughiar kam…®n itir gumazamizir kaba ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…® bizir kaba bar otivam.  
\v 35 \x - \xo 24:35 \xt Aisaia 40:8; Matyu 5:18; Mak 13:31; Luk 21:33\x*Overiam ko nguazim g…®vagham, eght…® nan m…®g…®r…®g…®aba g…®vaghan kogham.‚Äù 
\s1 Iesus ghaze, a ua izamin dughiam, tav a g…®fozir puvat…® 
\r (Mak 13:32-37; Luk 17:26-30; 17:34-36) 
\p  
\v 36 \x - \xo 24:36 \xt Sekaraia 14:7; Aposel 1:7; 1 Tesalonika 5:1-2\x*Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúBizir k…® ia m…®geir kaba otivamin dughiam, tav a g…®fozir puvat…®. Ensel…®n God…®n Nguibam…®n itiba ko God…®n Otarim uaghan fozir puvat…®. Afeziam bar uab…®ra fo.  
\v 37 \x - \xo 24:37 \xt Jenesis 6:5-8\x*Ez…® bizir Noan dughiam…®n otiviziba, da uaghan Gumazamizibar Otarim Izamin Dughiam…®n otivam.  
\v 38 \x - \xo 24:38 \xt Luk 17:26; 1 Pita 3:20\x*D…®par ekiar nguazim bar anevarazim t…®ghar izamin dughiam…®n, gumazamiziba dagheba ko d…®paba apa, uarir ikia mamagh…®ra iti. Me kamagh…®n amua ikiav itima, Noa kurim…®n aven ghu.  
\v 39 \x - \xo 24:39 \xt Jenesis 7:6-24; 2 Pita 3:6\x*Me bizir me bativamin tam g…®fozir puvat…®, egha pura ikiav itima, aperiar ekiam otogha bar me avaragha me avigha ghue. Gumazamizibar Otarim izamin dughiam, uaghan kamagh…®ram otivam.  
\v 40 Gumazir pumuning azenim…®n ik…®t…®, God tav inigh…®va tav ategham.  
\v 41 Amizir pumuning bretbar amus…® plaua m…®rm…®r ik…®t…®, God tav inigh…®va tav ategham. 
\p  
\v 42 \x - \xo 24:42 \xt Matyu 25:13; Mak 13:33; Luk 21:36\x*‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®, ia deragh gan ik…®. Ian Ekiam izamin dughiam, ia a g…®fozir puvat…®.  
\v 43 \x - \xo 24:43 \xt 1 Tesalonika 5:2; 2 Pita 3:10; Akar Mogomem 3:3; 16:15\x*\x - \xo 24:43-44 \xt Luk 12:39-40\x*Ia arazir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh. Gumazir manam, ok…®mak…®ar gumaziba d…®magarim…®n izava an d…®penim akarasava amima, a men dughiam g…®fogha, men arafa. Egha me ataghiz…® me an d…®penim akarizir puvat…®.  
\v 44 \x - \xo 24:44 \xt Matyu 25:13; 1 Tesalonika 5:6\x*Kamagh…®ra, ia uaghan aravagh ik…® gan. Guizbang…®ra, dughiar ia Gumazamizibar Otarim m…®zuaman koghamim, a dughiar kamram otogham.‚Äù 
\s1 Ingangarir gumazir aghuim ko ingangarir gumazir kuram…®n akar is…®n zuim 
\r (Luk 12:42-46) 
\p  
\v 45 Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIngangarir gumazir manamra n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba ikia derav…®ra uan ingangarim gami? An gumazir ekiam a damut…®, a ingangarir gumazir igharazibar ganam. Egh dughiar an gumazir ekiam ifongezim…®n, a dagheba is…® ingangarir gumazibar an…®ngam.  
\v 46 \x - \xo 24:46 \xt Akar Mogomem 16:15\x*Ingangarir gumazir kam ingara itima, an gumazir ekiam izava a batogha an ingangarir kam…®n garima, gumazir kam…®n navir averiam bar an dera.  
\v 47 \x - \xo 24:47 \xt Matyu 25:21-23\x*Ez…® k…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ingangarir gumazir kam…®n ekiam a damight…®ma, an an ingangarir gumazir mabar ekiam…®n ik…®va an biziba bar dar ganam.  
\v 48 Eght…® ingangarir gumazir kam guizbang…®ra ikuvigh, egh a uab…® kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gham, ‚ÄòNan ekiam zuam…®ra izeghan kogham.‚Äô  
\v 49 Egha uaghan a ko ingarir daraziv sogh, wain…®n d…®pabar am…® gumazir d…®par onganiba apiba ko ikiam.  
\v 50 Eght…® an ekiam, dughiar an ingangarir gumazim a bagha garir puvat…®zim…®n, an otogham. A dughiar a fozir puvat…®zim…®n uamategham.  
\v 51 \x - \xo 24:51 \xt Matyu 8:12; 25:30\x*Ingangarir gumazir kam…®n gumazir ekiam bar pazav, a damigh, ivezir bar kuram a dan…®ngam. Egh a is…®va ifavaribagh amir gumazibar tong…®n anet…®gham. Eght…® a danganir kam…®n ik…®va, arang atariba kuskugh mamagh…®ra ikiam.‚Äù 
\c 25  
\s1 Iesus 10plan guivir igiabar akar is…®n zuim m…®gei 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 25:1 \xt Luk 12:35; Akar Mogomem 19:7\x*Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam mati, guivir igiar 10plan eghaghanim…®n m…®n mangam. Gumazir mam igiamra amuim…®n ikiasa izi. Ez…® guivir igiar maba uan lamba inigha tuavim…®n an apuasa zui.  
\v 2 Men 5pla, n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba itima, 5pla n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba puvat…®.  
\v 3 Egha 5plan n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba itir puvat…®ziba, uan lamba isa, egha da bagha boretaba inizir puvat…®.\f + \fr 25:3 \ft Israel…®n adarazi oliv…®n borem isava, uan lambagh ruava dagh aboi, me en m…®n karasin lambagh aboir puvat…®.\f* 
\v 4 Ez…® guivir igiar n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba itiba, uan lamba isa, egha uaghan borem itir m…®sevir maba sara, ini.  
\v 5 Ez…® gumazir amuim…®n ikiamim zuam…®ra izezir puvat…®, ez…® guivir kaba pariam men azima, me akui. 
\p  
\v 6 ‚ÄúEz…® d…®magarir ar…®zim…®n gumazir mam d…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòGumazir amuim…®n ikiamim, a rogh…®ra izi. Ia iz…®, e mang…®, tuavim…®n a batogh a ko izam.‚Äô  
\v 7 Ez…® guivir igiar kaba d…®kavigha uan lambar k…®ri. 
\p  
\v 8 ‚ÄúEz…® guivir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba puvat…®ziba, n…®ghn…®zir aghuim itibar aza ghaze, ‚ÄòEn lamba mungasava ami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia boretaba e dan…®ngigh.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 9 ‚ÄúEz…® n…®ghn…®zir aghuim itir guiviba, me ikaragha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòPuvat…®gham! Borem bar en tughat…®ghan kogham. Ia mang…®, boreba amadir danganitam…®n uari bagh tabagh ivesegh.‚Äô  
\v 10 Ez…® guivir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba puvat…®zir kaba ghuez…®ma, gumazir amuim…®n ikiamim oto. Ez…® guivir boreba itiba, a ko isar ekiam bagha d…®penim…®n aven ghue. Ez…® gumaziba tiam asara. 
\p  
\v 11 \x - \xo 25:11-12 \xt Luk 13:25\x*‚ÄúEz…® g…®n guivir ghueziba uamategha iza kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòEkiam! Ekiam, n…® iz…® e bagh tiam kuigh.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 25:12 \xt Matyu 7:23\x*‚ÄúEz…® a me ikaragha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, k…® ia g…®fozir puvat…®.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 25:13 \xt Matyu 24:42-44; 1 Tesalonika 5:6; 1 Pita 5:8\x*Egha Iesus ghaze, ‚ÄúKamagh…®ra, ia deraghav…®ra gan. Ian Ekiam, aruem ko dughiar ia fozir puvat…®zim…®n, an otogham.‚Äù 
\s1 Ingangarir gumazibar dag…®aba inizim…®n, akar is…®n zuim 
\r (Luk 19:11-27) 
\p  
\v 14 \x - \xo 25:14 \xt Mak 13:34\x*Egha Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam mati, gumazir mam nguibar saghon itim…®n mangasava ami mok…®n. Gumazir kam uan ingangarir gumazibar diaz…® me izima, a uan biziba is…®, me danight…®ma, me a bagh dar ganam.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 25:15 \xt Rom 12:6\x*A gumazibar araziba ko gavgavibar gara, dag…®aba tuiragha da isa me gan…®ngi. A mav 5,000 kina a gan…®ga, mav 2,000 kina a gan…®ga, mav 1,000 kina a gan…®ngi. A kamagh…®n amigha ghu.  
\v 16 A ghuz…®ma, gumazir 5,000 kina inizim magh…®ra an ingara, 5,000 kinan mam a dagh is…®n uam a ini.  
\v 17 Ez…® gumazir 2,000 kina inizim kamagh…®ra amua, uaghan 2,000 kinan mam dagh is…®n uam a ini.  
\v 18 Ez…® gumazir 1,000 kina inizim ghua mozim okoregha uan gumazir ekiam…®n dag…®aba isa mozim gat…®gha da modo. 
\p  
\v 19 ‚ÄúEz…® gumazir ekiam dughiar ruarim…®n saghon ikegha uamategha ize. Egha uan ingangarir gumazibar ingangaribagh fofoghasa men dei.  
\v 20 Ez…® gumazir 5,000 kina inizim, 5,000 kinan mam a dibagha, a inigha iza kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòEkiam, n…® 5,000 kina na gan…®ngi. N…® ge, k…® dag…®ar ingangarim gamua, 5,000 kinan mam dagh is…®n uam a ini.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 21 \x - \xo 25:21 \xt Matyu 24:45-47; Luk 12:44; 16:10; 2 Timoti 2:12\x*‚ÄúEz…® an ekiam kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® ingangarir gumazir aghuim, n…® ingangarir aghuim gami. N…® bizir doziba derav…®ra dar gari. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, n…® ingangarir ekiabar ganasa, k…® ifonge. N…® iz…® uan ekiam…®n isam…®n aven ik…®, egh a ko bar akuegham.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 22 ‚ÄúEz…® gumazir 2,000 kina inizim iza kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòEkiam, n…® 2,000 kina na gan…®ngi. N…® ge, k…® dag…®ar ingangarim gamua, 2,000 kinan mam dagh is…®n uam a ini.‚Äô  
\v 23 Ez…® an ekiam kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® ingangarir gumazir aghuim, n…® ingangarir aghuim gami. N…® bizir doziba derav…®ra dar gari. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® ingangarir ekiabar ganasa, k…® ifonge. N…® iz…®, uan ekiam…®n isam…®n aven ik…®, egh a ko bar akuegham.‚Äô 
